text: Turrilatirus craticulatus is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Fasciolariidae, the spindle snails, the tulip snails and their allies. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Fasciolariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1758 Category:Taxa named by Carl Linnaeus
title: Turrilatirus craticulatus
